INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (71, 20, 'project_manager', 'Be sure to send the Creative Questionnaire to Client prior to the Collaborative Discovery Session.\r\n\r\nBe sure to find out the brass tacks of the presentation: who is the audience? Where will it be delivered? Is there a single use or will the entire sales force have it? What types of computers and software will they be using (Mac/PC, what version of PowerPoint or Keynote)? You get the idea.') ; 
