INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (499, 71, 'project_manager', 'Two agendas are created for the Collaborative Discovery Session: a detailed one for internal use, and a broader one for the Client.\r\n\r\nThe Content Developer owns both of these agendas, but the Project Manager will deliver the external agenda to the Client <i>prior </i>to the meeting. Review the Internal Kickoff Summary document to make sure all relevant issues and questions are being addressed.\r\nArtifact: IN_Sample Discovery Agenda.docx\r\n\r\nThe Project Manager should distribute both the internal and external agenda in advance of any meetings with Content Developers so they\'ve got time to prepare. The Sample Discovery Agenda is a good format for the creation of both internal and external agendas.\r\nArtifact: IN_Sample Discovery Agenda.docx') ; 
