INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (2135, 196, 'project_manager', 'If the Design Lead needs any help putting together a Production Checklist, lend some of your mad spreadsheet skills to the task!\r\n\r\nIf the checklist lives on the web (in a Google Spreadsheet, for example) you can have multiple people marking progress simultaneously—you and the Design Lead, probably.\r\n\r\nOnce the checklist is complete, use it to calculate how much time you\'ll need from the different skillsets (Photoshop, PowerPoint, etc), and make sure you have the resources you need to get the job done.\r\n\r\nMaintain good communication with your Design Lead here as you select resources to ensure a good fit for the tasks required. If you notice a large amount of work of a similar type needs to be done, perhaps start conversations with potential resources and their PM\'s in advance to lock down a big chunk of their time. You\'ll get much more consistency if you have a single resource making, say, and icon set, than if you have multiple designers creating the different pieces.') ; 
