INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (4850, 470, 'project_manager', 'Have client send the PO to purchaseorders@duarte.com and cc the Account Manager and Project Manager. Purchaseorders@duarte.com is received by all accounting personnel.\r\n\r\nPO documents/emails are to be attached in Filemaker to the corresponding job# Documents field). This is especially important for new clients. Screenshot: PO_Document.jpg\r\n\r\nEnter the PO # in the billing tab in Filemaker and indicate how much of the PO you are using in the budget field (even if it\'s just an estimate). This helps the accounting department recognize revenue / track the burn rate. Screenshot: PO_Info.jpg\r\n\r\nAt earliest opportunity, obtain Accounts Payable (AP) information from the client and input into Filemaker. This is tremendously helpful to the Duarte Accounting team and will save everyone time later. Don\'t assume if you work on another project with the same client that this information will be the same. Re-verify AP info in case main contact has left the company or a different AP department is to be used.') ; 
