INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (6024, 586, 'project_manager', 'The Project Manager should set up an FTP / RELAY (<a href="http://relay.duarte.com" target="_blank">http://relay.duarte.com</a>) login for the client, and e-mail the log in and password to the client.\r\n\r\nFor Studio / Studio Lite projects, create and distribute the Project Contact List with names/contact info for Clients as well as key Duarte personnel (President, VP, Account Director, Account Manager, Project Manager). Artifact: EX_Key Contacts List.docx\r\n\r\nIdentify the client\'s technical requirements (the Account Manager may already have them) and distribute to the relevant creative teams. Use the Client Technical Requirements artifact for reference. Artifact: IN_Technological Requirements.docx\r\n\r\nIf the Project Manager will be traveling for the project, s/he should communicate with the Office Manager/Travel Agent to make the necessary arrangements. Review the Travel Checklist to cover all bases. Artifact: IN_Travel Checklist.docx\r\n\r\nProvide all source materials to resources/team prior to workshop and/or kickoff. Review Internal Kickoff Checklist to ensure all possible issues are considered in the Internal Kickoff Meeting.  Artifact: IN_Kickoff Checklist.docx\r\n\r\nFormulate and distribute to all internal team members the Internal Kickoff Summary document, which identifies all relevant issues and questions to pose to client. This document should be used to help formulate the Discovery / Workshop agendas. Artifact: IN_Kickoff Summary.docx') ; 
